text: Henriette Parzer (born 28 August 1943) is an Austrian gymnast. She competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
